U2ZSdzBvDqzgI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recOeHZYvDGUbB794","target":"recgdvRbWEPMp5I0z","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recOeHZYvDGUbB794","target":"recEP3QZ3HUmIkv4Q","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recOeHZYvDGUbB794","target":"rec6VHpWbv15YXzKg","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recOeHZYvDGUbB794","target":"recJK76HLZSOzxTWW","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recOeHZYvDGUbB794","target":"recdm9AlLF01lFAfP","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recOeHZYvDGUbB794","target":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recOeHZYvDGUbB794","target":"rec34nlC2Rt0dlYyu","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recOeHZYvDGUbB794","target":"recEwQ7ucCWe9yVvi","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recOeHZYvDGUbB794","target":"rec0MJooZFfHsxW1N","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recmRN20Rl2ZvMNpG","ref":"Amos.4.1","text":"Hear this word, ye kine of Bashan, that are in the mountain of Samaria, which oppress the poor, which crush the needy, which say to their masters, Bring, and let us drink.","year":-787},{"id":"recIk6tC9aVfJo7dm","ref":"Amos.4.2","text":"The Lord GOD hath sworn by his holiness, that, lo, the days shall come upon you, that he will take you away with hooks, and your posterity with fishhooks.","year":-787},{"id":"recOMh0mQqpyTpcrV","ref":"Amos.4.3","text":"And ye shall go out at the breaches, every cow at that which is before her; and ye shall cast them into the palace, saith the LORD.","year":-787},{"id":"recDOtqub0Es7qIgq","ref":"Amos.4.4","text":"Come to Bethel, and transgress; at Gilgal multiply transgression; and bring your sacrifices every morning, and your tithes after three years:","year":-787},{"id":"recLJmo3U3dg07eci","ref":"Amos.4.5","text":"And offer a sacrifice of thanksgiving with leaven, and proclaim and publish the free offerings: for this liketh you, O ye children of Israel, saith the Lord GOD.","year":-787},{"id":"recsqzl6SMvGSlFsh","ref":"Amos.4.6","text":"And I also have given you cleanness of teeth in all your cities, and want of bread in all your places: yet have ye not returned unto me, saith the LORD.","year":-787},{"id":"rec2B3U9gExaLhPp2","ref":"Amos.4.7","text":"And also I have withholden the rain from you, when there were yet three months to the harvest: and I caused it to rain upon one city, and caused it not to rain upon another city: one piece was rained upon, and the piece whereupon it rained not withered.","year":-787},{"id":"reck4dmdrpk0ftl60","ref":"Amos.4.8","text":"So two or three cities wandered unto one city, to drink water; but they were not satisfied: yet have ye not returned unto me, saith the LORD.","year":-787}]}
